{
  "startNodeId": "start",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "text": "你在一片迷雾中醒来，四周一片寂静。远处隐约可见一座古老的森林，森林深处似乎有微弱的光芒闪烁。你不知道自己是如何来到这里的，只记得一个名字——回声之境。一阵寒风吹过，你裹紧了身上的斗篷，决定开始探索这片神秘的土地。",
      "background": "misty_forest.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_wind",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_forest",
          "text": "向着古老森林前进",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_edge",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "path_taken", "value": "forest" },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_light",
          "text": "追寻那道微弱的光芒",
          "nextNodeId": "mysterious_light",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "path_taken", "value": "light" },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "curiosity", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_stay",
          "text": "原地等待，观察周围",
          "nextNodeId": "waiting",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "patience", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "forest_edge",
      "text": "你来到了森林的边缘。巨大的古树直插云霄，树皮上刻满了奇异的符文。空气中弥漫着潮湿的泥土气息和不知名花朵的芬芳。一只银色的狐狸从树丛中探出头来，用充满智慧的眼睛看着你，似乎在等待着什么。",
      "background": "ancient_forest.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_forest",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_follow_fox",
          "text": "跟随银狐深入森林",
          "nextNodeId": "fox_guide",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "has_guide", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "trust", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_go_alone",
          "text": "独自探索森林",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_depths",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "independence", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_examine_runes",
          "text": "仔细研究树皮上的符文",
          "nextNodeId": "rune_study",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "knowledge", "value": 2 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "knows_runes", "value": true }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "mysterious_light",
      "text": "你向着光芒的方向走去，穿过一片开阔的草地。光芒越来越亮，最后你发现它来自一座漂浮在空中的水晶塔。塔的周围环绕着彩色的光晕，如梦似幻。塔底有一扇半开的门，似乎在邀请你进入。",
      "background": "crystal_tower.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_magic",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_enter_tower",
          "text": "进入水晶塔",
          "nextNodeId": "tower_entrance",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "curiosity", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_circle_tower",
          "text": "绕塔一周观察",
          "nextNodeId": "tower_surroundings",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "caution", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "found_secret", "value": true }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_call_out",
          "text": "大声呼喊，询问是否有人",
          "nextNodeId": "echo_response",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "bravery", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "waiting",
      "text": "你选择原地等待，仔细观察四周。时间慢慢流逝，迷雾逐渐散去，你看到了更多的细节。不远处有一条小径，路旁有一块石碑，上面似乎刻着文字。渐渐地，你听到了远处传来的脚步声，有人正在向这边走来。",
      "background": "misty_path.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_wind",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_read_stone",
          "text": "去查看石碑上的文字",
          "nextNodeId": "stone_tablet",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "knowledge", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_hide",
          "text": "躲起来观察来人",
          "nextNodeId": "hidden_observer",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "stealth", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "saw_stranger", "value": true }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_greet",
          "text": "主动上前打招呼",
          "nextNodeId": "meeting_stranger",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 2 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fox_guide",
      "text": "银狐转身向森林深处走去，不时回头看看你是否跟上。你们穿过一片又一片的树林，最后来到了一个宁静的湖泊旁。湖水清澈见底，湖中央有一座小岛，岛上有一棵发光的树。银狐跳入湖中，游向小岛，然后站在岸边回头望向你。",
      "background": "enchanted_lake.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_water",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_swim",
          "text": "跟着银狐游向小岛",
          "nextNodeId": "island_tree",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_shore",
          "text": "在岸边等待",
          "nextNodeId": "lake_shore_wait",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "patience", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_look_boat",
          "text": "寻找船只或其他渡河方式",
          "nextNodeId": "find_boat",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "forest_depths",
      "text": "你独自深入森林，周围的树木越来越茂密，光线也越来越暗。突然，你听到了一阵低沉的咆哮声，一只巨大的暗影狼出现在你面前，它的眼睛闪烁着红色的光芒。它似乎在守护着什么，不让你继续前进。",
      "background": "dark_forest.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_rain",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_fight",
          "text": "勇敢地面对暗影狼",
          "nextNodeId": "wolf_confrontation",
          "condition": { "variable": "courage", "operator": ">=", "value": 2 },
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "defeated_wolf", "value": true }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_retreat",
          "text": "慢慢后退，寻找其他路径",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_detour",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "caution", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_communicate",
          "text": "尝试与暗影狼沟通",
          "nextNodeId": "wolf_dialogue",
          "condition": { "variable": "knowledge", "operator": ">=", "value": 2 },
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "wolf_friend", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 3 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "rune_study",
      "text": "你仔细研究树皮上的符文，发现它们记载着关于这片土地的古老传说。据说回声之境是连接现实与梦境的边界，每个来到这里的人都需要找到自己内心的回声。符文还提到了三件圣物：勇气之心、智慧之眼和友谊之链，集齐它们可以打开通往真相的大门。",
      "background": "rune_tree.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_forest",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_continue_deeper",
          "text": "带着符文的知识继续深入",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_depths",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "knowledge", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_seek_artifacts",
          "text": "开始寻找三件圣物",
          "nextNodeId": "artifact_quest",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "artifact_quest_started", "value": true }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_go_back_start",
          "text": "返回迷雾处重新选择方向",
          "nextNodeId": "start",
          "effects": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "tower_entrance",
      "text": "你走进水晶塔，内部比外面看起来要大得多。墙壁上镶嵌着无数的水晶，散发出柔和的光芒。大厅中央有一个巨大的沙漏，沙子正在缓缓流动。沙漏旁边站着一位身穿白色长袍的老者，他转过身来，用深邃的眼睛看着你。",
      "background": "tower_interior.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_magic",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_ask_elder",
          "text": "询问老者这是什么地方",
          "nextNodeId": "elder_explanation",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "knowledge", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_examine_hourglass",
          "text": "仔细观察沙漏",
          "nextNodeId": "hourglass_mystery",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "curiosity", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_touch_crystal",
          "text": "触碰墙上的水晶",
          "nextNodeId": "crystal_vision",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "had_vision", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "stone_tablet",
      "text": "你走到石碑旁，拂去上面的灰尘，露出了古老的文字。上面写着：\"回声之境，心之所向。勇者无畏，智者不惑，仁者无敌。三者合一，方能归家。\" 你沉思着这些话的含义，似乎有什么重要的东西被遗忘了。",
      "background": "stone_tablet.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_wind",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_forest_path",
          "text": "沿着小径走向森林",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_edge",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_light_path",
          "text": "朝着远处的光芒前进",
          "nextNodeId": "mysterious_light",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_meditate",
          "text": "在石碑旁打坐冥想",
          "nextNodeId": "meditation_vision",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 2 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "had_vision", "value": true }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "meeting_stranger",
      "text": "你主动走上前去打招呼。来人是一位年轻的旅人，名叫艾拉。她也是被迷雾带到这里的，已经在这片土地上探索了好几天。她很高兴遇到了同伴，并愿意与你分享她发现的信息。她说在东边有一座古老的神殿，也许能找到离开这里的方法。",
      "background": "meeting_companion.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_forest",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_team_up",
          "text": "与艾拉结伴同行",
          "nextNodeId": "journey_together",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "has_companion", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 3 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_go_separate",
          "text": "道谢后各自行动",
          "nextNodeId": "solo_journey",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "independence", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_ask_more_info",
          "text": "向她询问更多信息",
          "nextNodeId": "ella_information",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "knowledge", "value": 2 },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "island_tree",
      "text": "你鼓起勇气跳入湖中，冰冷的湖水让你打了个寒颤，但你还是奋力游向了小岛。爬上岛后，你来到了那棵发光的树下。树干上有一个树洞，里面放着一颗心形的宝石，散发着温暖的光芒。银狐蹲坐在树旁，似乎在等你做出选择。",
      "background": "glowing_tree.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_magic",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_take_heart",
          "text": "取走心形容宝石",
          "nextNodeId": "heart_artifact",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "has_courage_heart", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 3 },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "artifact_count", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_leave_heart",
          "text": "不触碰任何东西，静静感受",
          "nextNodeId": "tree_wisdom",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 3 },
            { "type": "set", "variable": "tree_blessing", "value": true }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wolf_confrontation",
      "text": "你鼓起勇气，直视着暗影狼的眼睛，没有丝毫退缩。令人惊讶的是，暗影狼的眼神中竟然出现了一丝赞许。它慢慢低下头，让你抚摸它的头。原来这只狼是森林的守护者，它在测试你的勇气。通过考验后，它愿意带你去森林最深处的秘密之地。",
      "background": "wolf_friend.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_forest",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_follow_wolf",
          "text": "跟随暗影狼前往秘密之地",
          "nextNodeId": "secret_grove",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "wolf_companion", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 2 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_go_own_way",
          "text": "感谢狼后继续自己的旅程",
          "nextNodeId": "deep_forest_path",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "independence", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "artifact_quest",
      "text": "你决定开始寻找三件圣物的旅程。根据符文的记载，勇气之心在森林深处，智慧之眼在水晶塔顶，友谊之链则需要你找到真正的朋友才能获得。你站在森林入口处，思考着应该先从哪里开始。",
      "background": "quest_start.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_wind",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_forest_first",
          "text": "先去森林寻找勇气之心",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_edge",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_tower_first",
          "text": "先去水晶塔寻找智慧之眼",
          "nextNodeId": "mysterious_light",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_find_friend",
          "text": "先寻找志同道合的伙伴",
          "nextNodeId": "meeting_stranger",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "elder_explanation",
      "text": "老者告诉你，这里是回声之境，每个来到这里的人都是迷失了自我的灵魂。要离开这里，必须找到属于自己的回声——也就是真实的自己。他说水晶塔里藏着智慧之眼，能够看穿一切幻象。但要得到它，必须通过他的考验。",
      "background": "elder_sage.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_magic",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_accept_test",
          "text": "接受老者的考验",
          "nextNodeId": "wisdom_test",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_ask_other_way",
          "text": "询问是否有其他方法",
          "nextNodeId": "other_paths",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "curiosity", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_leave_tower",
          "text": "暂时离开，再做考虑",
          "nextNodeId": "mysterious_light",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "caution", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "journey_together",
      "text": "你和艾拉决定结伴同行。一路上，你们分享着各自的故事和发现。艾拉告诉你，她在来这里之前是一名画家，她觉得自己失去了创作的灵感，然后就在一片迷雾中醒来了。你们的友谊在旅途中逐渐加深。",
      "background": "travel_together.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_forest",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_go_temple",
          "text": "一起前往古老神殿",
          "nextNodeId": "ancient_temple",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "friendship", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_explore_forest",
          "text": "先探索附近的森林",
          "nextNodeId": "forest_edge",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "courage", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_find_tower",
          "text": "去寻找传说中的水晶塔",
          "nextNodeId": "mysterious_light",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wisdom_test",
      "text": "老者的考验开始了。他问了你三个问题：什么是真实？什么是幸福？什么是勇气？你需要在心中给出自己的答案。每个问题都没有标准答案，重要的是你是否真正理解了自己。",
      "background": "wisdom_test.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_magic",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_true_self",
          "text": "遵从本心，如实回答",
          "nextNodeId": "pass_test",
          "condition": { "variable": "wisdom", "operator": ">=", "value": 2 },
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "has_wisdom_eye", "value": true },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 2 },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "artifact_count", "value": 1 }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_think_deep",
          "text": "深思熟虑后再回答",
          "nextNodeId": "partial_pass",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "add", "variable": "wisdom", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "add", "variable": "patience", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ancient_temple",
      "text": "你和艾拉来到了古老的神殿前。神殿由巨大的石柱支撑，门上雕刻着复杂的图案。推开门，神殿中央有一个祭坛，上面放着一条闪闪发光的项链。祭坛两侧的墙壁上刻着文字：\"真正的友谊，是穿越迷雾的灯塔。\"",
      "background": "ancient_temple.jpg",
      "ambientSound": "ambient_wind",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_take_necklace",
          "text": "与艾拉一起取走项链",
          "nextNodeId": "friendship_chains",
          "condition": { "variable": "friendship", "operator": ">=", "value": 5 },
          "effects": [
            { "type": "set", "variable": "has_friendship_chain", "value": true },
